










 




Energy Trust Partners



































Since 2002, the Energy Trust Partners funds ("ETP") have been providing private equity capital to oil and gas companies led by experienced and capable management teams. The professionals at ETP and their affiliates have managed and invested in excess of $6.5 billion in the energy business since 1981.



















