BlueJack Energy Solutions





  Status: Active
  Headquarters: Frisco, TX
www.bluejackenergy.com

  Formed in April 2016, BlueJack Energy Solutions provides waste management solutions to oil and gas producers with a particular focus on water gathering and disposal, solids processing and disposal, and wastewater recycling. BlueJack has a long-term, fee-based contract to provide wastewater management services to Laredo Petroleum (NYSE: LPI) in Glasscock and Reagan counties in the Midland Basin of West Texas.
  



Active
