Caliche Development Partners





  Status: Active
  Headquarters: Houston, TX
www.calichestorage.com

  Formed in May 2016, Caliche Development Partners will develop, construct and operate underground hydrocarbon storage facilities at salt cavern sites in North America. Caliche plans to target both development and acquisition opportunities, with an initial focus on development of NGL storage on the U.S. Gulf Coast.
  



