Stonehenge Energy Resources II





  Status: Active
  Headquarters: Westminster, CO
www.stonehengeenergy.com

  In May 2015, Stonehenge Energy Resources ("Stonehenge") entered into an agreement with Rex Energy Corporation (NASDAQ: REXX) to develop a natural gas gathering, compression and dehydration system in the Marcellus Shale. The system will include ~65 miles of pipeline with total capacity of ~500+ MMcf/d with a target in-service date of January 2016.
  



