Dornick Hills Midstream





  Status: Realized
  Headquarters: Dallas, TX

  Dornick Hills Midstream was formed in November 2004 to acquire a natural gas gathering system and processing plant near Sherman, TX from Dynegy. The Company sold those assets to SemGas, the natural gas business unit of the SemGroup, in October 2006.
  



Realized
Enerven Compression





  Status: Realized
  Headquarters: Dallas, TX
www.enerven.com

  In August 2005, ESC acquired a majority interest in Enerven from one of its prior owners. At the time, Enerven operated a small rental compression fleet, and a third party compression maintenance business through its wholly-owned subsidiary Wesco. ESC provided additional capital to Enerven to support its strategy of growing its rental compression fleet by acquiring and deploying new compression units. In April 2008, after having significantly grown the size of its rental compression fleet, ESC sold its interest in Enerven to two institutional investors and existing Enerven management.
  



